Package: swissparl
Type: Package
Title: Interface to the Webservices of the Swiss Parliament and the
        OpenParlData.ch REST API
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("David", "Zumbach", , "david.zumbach@gfzb.ch", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Benjamin", "Gföhler", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides machine-readable access to parliamentary data of the 
    Swiss Federal Assembly via the official OData interface ([https://ws.parlament.ch/odata.svc/](https://ws.parlament.ch/odata.svc/)) 
    and the OpenParlData REST API ([https://api.openparldata.ch](https://api.openparldata.ch/documentation)), which also 
    offers harmonized data for selected cantonal and municipal parliaments.
URL: https://www.parlament.ch/en/services/open-data-webservices,
        https://api.openparldata.ch
BugReports: https://github.com/zumbov2/swissparl/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: dplyr, jsonlite, magrittr, purrr, stringr, tibble, tidyr,
        crayon, httr, ggplot2, glue, utils
NeedsCompilation: no
